1. *Ispred* mene je stajalo troje dece. (In front of me, three children were standing.) 
2. *Ispred* nas je bio veliki park. (In front of us, there was a large park.)
3. Ona je stajala *ispred* zgrade. (She was standing in front of the building.)
4. Prošao sam kroz vrata *ispred* kojih je stajala. (I went through the door in front of which she was standing.)
5. Oni su šetali *ispred* zgrade. (They were walking in front of the building.)
6. Stajao sam *ispred* njega. (I was standing in front of him.)